<h2 class="bac">Training:</h2>
<p class="bac">
Associates will participate in a formal Education and Orientation program to learn more about Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America, the culture and values, as well as to network with Executives and other campus hires.  Additionally, associates will participate in various networking and learning opportunities throughout the duration of the program. 
</p>

